            <Box name="Get Age" id="1" localization="8" tooltip="This box returns the age of the person in front of the robot.&#x0A;The detection fails when there are more or less than one person in front of the robot or when the timeout is exceeded.&#x0A;&#x0A;It is possible to set up the Confidence Threshold and the Timeout parameters for this box. " x="387" y="151">
